textContent:
---taylor swift---

You can hear it in the silence because even when I'm alone, I still hear your voice, your laugh, and the small expressions that you make.

You can feel it in the way home because when we're in that situation, I don't want the moment to end. Even if I know I'll see you again.

You can see it with the lights out because whenever I close my eyes, I could easily recall your wide smile, your beautiful eyes, and the dimples on your cheeks.
